body:
Looks like a missing Python module in tf.contrib :(. Adding the following lines [here](https://github.com/martinwicke/tensorflow/blob/0daa5a0a2ce3c695b94a7008b191780343010bdc/tensorflow/contrib/cmake/tf_python.cmake#L313) should get you there:

```
add_python_module("tensorflow/contrib/legacy_seq2seq/python")
add_python_module("tensorflow/contrib/legacy_seq2seq/python/ops")
```
